caption.body: NOW PLAYING: London-based filmmaker Annlin Chao’s stop-motion animated short features a shapeshifting character who journeys through a sequence of landscapes representing four masterpieces of Chinese painting held in Taiwan’s National Palace Museum  See "Traveling Through Brush and Ink" by Annlin Chao, now playing in the Video Arts Room located pre-security in the International Terminal. http://bit.ly/2WfboNG
